Accessing Small SkewLeftBrace AllSmallSkewLeftBrace is an accessor function for accessing the complete list of non-isomorphic SkewLeftBrace of orders 2 to 3.
<#Include Label = "AllSmallSkewLeftBrace">
The output skewleftbrace are represented by its operation table for +, *, as given in Section .

Checking Models of Small SkewLeftBrace
"IsASmallSkewLeftBrace" is a function for checking a model against the complete list of non-isomorphic SkewLeftBrace of orders 2 to 3. It returns true if the model is a Small SkewLeftBrace, false otherwise.
